tasks.implementationGuide:
1. pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add command dialog textarea separator 실행
2. types/analyze.ts 생성:
   - AnalyzeStep: 'select-a' | 'select-b' | 'ready' | 'analyzing' | 'result'
   - SlotData: { type: 'product' | 'manual', productId?: string, productName?: string, brand?: string, ingredients?: string[] }
   - AnalyzeState: { step: AnalyzeStep, slotA: SlotData | null, slotB: SlotData | null }
   - AnalyzeAction: union type (SELECT_SLOT_A, SELECT_SLOT_B, START_ANALYZE, SET_RESULT, RESET)
   - ConflictResult: { ingredientA: string, ingredientB: string, conflictType: 'avoid' | 'caution', severity: 'high' | 'medium' | 'low', reasonKo: string, recommend: string }
   - SynergyResult: { ingredientA: string, ingredientB: string, reasonKo: string }
   - AnalyzeResult: { conflicts: ConflictResult[], synergies: SynergyResult[] }
